<title>FRANCE: Ford to build Ka car in Brazil.</title>
<headline>Ford to build Ka car in Brazil.</headline>
<dateline>PARIS 1996-09-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ford Motor Co chairman Alex Trotman said on Monday the company planned to produce its Ka minicar in Brazil.</p>
<p>Trotman, in Paris for a car show, said the company currently produced the car at its plant in Valencia, Spain, which has capacity for 200,000 Ka cars a year.</p>
<p>Trotman gave no further details about Ford's plan to produce the car in Brazil.</p>
<p>-- Paris Newsroom +331 4221 5452</p>
